{"tid":1705781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打工仔同我入黎] 想嬴嘅由聽日開始幫我做一樣嘢 要日日做","createTime":"2019-11-11T02:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T03:24:13.000Z","uid":84408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10c9693684c59d1a4c7a8410d89eb5868c56914c","tid":1705781,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"職工盟暫不呼籲罷工 正協助更多新工會籌備工作<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191111/s00001/1573410821043/%E7%B6%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191111%2Fs00001%2F1573410821043%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=d742ad22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191111%2Fs00001%2F1573410821043%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2&h=792698ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20191111/s00001/1573410821043/%E7%B6%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n又係我呢個煩膠和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就黎變到一日一po<br />\n我已經見到有人響度屌職工盟大台左膠<br />\n我同你地講 佢地嘅同事響呢場運動幫咗好多新工會成立<br />\n人地話唔罷工係因為時機未到<br />\n<br />\n你班速食主義撚就響度屌<br />\n有無諗過點搞一場成功嘅罷工啊?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係日日叫你啲同事入會啊</span></span><br />\n今日朝早開花一戰 已經正視聽好多次<br />\n講左唔係三罷 加上人地都無意做大台<br />\n你地就剩係識屌<br />\n有無幫助過罷工成事啊?<br />\n<br />\n唔急但要快 就黎講到口臭<br />\n罷工係要好多時間 再日日咁樣快閃開花法<br />\n未光復香港 啲手足已經死撚哂<br />\n<br />\n我都講過波蘭工會之所以成事<br />\n佢一年內儲左一千萬會員<br />\n平均三分之一打工仔人口<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔該要返工嘅人<br />\n同我聽日開始組織會員</span></span>"},{"pid":"93649b7e5e2bc7b7dc6ad56324011cc1d01f4101","tid":1705781,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"今次美國議員已經出左聲<br />\n求大家幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n最新：tag左英國議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1193698691212828673?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1193698691212828673%3Fs%3D20&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=96b8ed2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1193698691212828673%3Fs%3D20&h=8f50b24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1193698691212828673?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n最新：又一個美國參議員出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1193714257172615168?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1193714257172615168%3Fs%3D19&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=960cf597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1193714257172615168%3Fs%3D19&h=29a7cd9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1193714257172615168?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n其他請入去幫推<br />\nTwitter 今朝 英美戰線 (跪求大家幫推）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"60ac4d74c81b120756a979b5261f6170c4af5806","tid":1705781,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b2f9d1bb78841803952c8b56feadeeacd9803e","tid":1705781,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:46:05.000Z","msg":"一定要搞工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0963997b0368e1cd214aa3ac1d9e728dd4d3cd1","tid":1705781,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif